OL,3,CExplosion and fire kill at least 15 at
OL,4,CIndia pharmaceutical plant
OL,6,FA large explosion set off by a fire at
OL,7,Fa Southern Indian pharmaceutical plant
OL,8,Fhas killed at least 15 workers and
OL,9,Finjured dozens more, police said.
OL,11,FAlongside those killed, another 40
OL,12,Fwere wounded and hospitalised in the
OL,13,Fblast and fire in the plant's chemical
OL,14,Freactor. Some of those injured are in
OL,15,Fa critical condition.
OL,17,FOfficers suspect the cause of the
OL,18,Fblast was related to electricity at
OL,19,Fthe plant. Authorities have launched
OL,20,Fan investigation.
