OL,3,CExplosion and fire kill at least 15 at
OL,4,CIndia pharmaceutical plant
OL,6,FThe explosion occurred at the
OL,7,FEscientia Company in Anakapalle
OL,8,Fdistrict. The plant is about 220 miles
OL,9,Fnortheast of Amaravati, the capital of
OL,10,FAndhra Pradesh.
OL,12,FThe five-year-old company manufactures
OL,13,Fintermediate chemicals and active
OL,14,Fpharmaceutical ingredients.
OL,16,FAs the news of the blast spread,
OL,17,Fhundreds of workers' family members
OL,18,Fand relatives rushed to the plant to
OL,19,Flearn what happened to their loved
OL,20,Fones.
